<h1 lang="en">Privacy Policy</h1>
<p lang="en"><strong>Perkotek PDKS</strong> (“App”) is provided by <strong>Perkotek</strong>. This page explains how your information is processed when you use the App.</p>

<div class="note" lang="en">
  Note: This policy covers the App only. Third‑party services (e.g., Firebase Cloud Messaging) are subject to their own policies.
</div>

<h2 lang="en">Data We Collect</h2>
<ul>
  <li lang="en"><strong>Camera</strong>: The App uses <code>android.permission.CAMERA</code> to scan QR/barcodes. The camera feed is processed <em>on‑device</em>; no photos/videos are <strong>stored</strong> or <strong>sent to servers</strong>.</li>
  <li lang="en"><strong>Notification Token (optional)</strong>: If notifications are enabled, Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM) may generate a device/app instance identifier (token). This token is used solely to deliver notifications.</li>
</ul>

<h2 lang="en">How We Use Data</h2>
<ul>
  <li lang="en">Camera data is used only for real‑time scanning.</li>
  <li lang="en">FCM token (if any) is used only for push delivery.</li>
</ul>

<h2 lang="en">Sharing</h2>
<p lang="en">We do not sell personal data and do not share it with third parties for marketing. We may disclose information when required by law.</p>

<h2 lang="en">Security</h2>
<p lang="en">We apply reasonable technical and organizational measures. Since the camera stream does not leave the device, no persistent remote storage occurs.</p>

<h2 lang="en">Children’s Privacy</h2>
<p lang="en">The App is not directed to children under 13.</p>

<h2 lang="en">Your Rights & Contact</h2>
<p lang="en">For privacy requests, contact: <a href="mailto:rauf@perkotek.com">rauf@perkotek.com</a></p>

<h2 lang="en">Third‑Party Services</h2>
<ul>
  <li lang="en">Firebase Cloud Messaging (Google LLC)</li>
</ul>

<footer lang="en">Effective date: 2025-08-27</footer>
